{"tid":1946869,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳馬雲 柳傳志聯署促習釋放任志強","createTime":"2020-03-28T01:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T11:30:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"57f1902107d55d31923b3dffb8d849a2e1255b85","tid":1946869,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200328/XZ6IGPYIDZUNOOJQ23NYTJIFHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200328%2FXZ6IGPYIDZUNOOJQ23NYTJIFHA%2F&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fkYzBSotcsoJ75UENuGtOl4%3D&h=68ccadf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200328%2FXZ6IGPYIDZUNOOJQ23NYTJIFHA%2F&h=7c780045\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200328/XZ6IGPYIDZUNOOJQ23NYTJIFHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n傳馬雲 柳傳志聯署促習釋放任志強<br />\n<br />\n早前以「剝光衣服堅持當皇帝的小丑」嘲諷中共總書記習近平的內地房地產商任志強，據稱已被北京市紀委立案調查。與此同時，Twitter昨流傳多位知名企業家集體上書習近平，向當今政權提出九大訴求。不過，聯署信的署名被遮蓋，未能證實其真偽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200328/large/1585324617_b967.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200328%2Flarge%2F1585324617_b967.gif&h=9e9e3489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任志強<br />\n<br />\n可信度低 或反習派造勢<br />\n<br />\n社交網站Twitter流傳，有人聲稱收到來自任志強友人的爆料，貼出共六頁的致習近平公開信。聯署者聲稱是一群企業家，指疫情「暴露了中國體制的一系列弱點」，提出九大訴求，分別為：堅持鄧小平改革開放路線，全盤否定文革，開啟政改和賦予人民一人一票的參政議政權利，公平對待民營企業，保護企業家的財產和人身安全，向全民發現金紓民困，問責官員處理疫情失當的責任，釋放任志強，以及重新調查李文亮事件。網絡流傳，聯署者包括阿里巴巴創辦人馬雲和聯想集團創辦人柳傳志。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員劉銳紹指出，這封署名遭遮蓋的公開信，就恍如早前陽光衞視董事長陳平轉發無人署名的建議書，要求中共高層召開緊急擴大會議討論習近平的功過和去留問題。他指目前沒有證據顯示民營企業家已凝聚起來，「連香港的李嘉誠也不會提出政治訴求，何況內地的企業家？」但他指近日海外網上不時有這些訊息出現，推斷有一股對習近平不滿的力量正蠢蠢欲動；習的支持者也可能「引蛇出洞」，把潛在反對勢力一網打盡。<br />\n<br />\n內地獨立記者高瑜分析，網上流傳多位知名企業家上書習近平，甚至還言之鑿鑿地稱有五名退休中共高層上書中央，可信度非常低。她表示美國有人向她「推薦」這些小道消息，但認為內容「基本上是編造」。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台/《蘋果》記者"},{"pid":"ba0f6116d5fb40486f04998d3f8e13a8a8407517","tid":1946869,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"馬雲只係幫黨國守財嘅守財奴<br />\n<br />\n如果背叛主子就準備被自殺啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2445000/2448438/jack_ma_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2445000%2F2448438%2Fjack_ma_1024.png&h=d24afa45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2155000/2157515/ma_thumb_20180910_E_V2_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2155000%2F2157515%2Fma_thumb_20180910_E_V2_1024.jpg&h=e47f2d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180911/s00004/c4ac70a1a7053c6418dd603e0b9de537.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180911%2Fs00004%2Fc4ac70a1a7053c6418dd603e0b9de537.jpg&h=e106a065&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee2ee5b5887098f155b85049bdd1c480b114a0ed","tid":1946869,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"捉埋呢兩個啦"},{"pid":"1a722eb970cee55136aae1a925fa3899b97716b7","tid":1946869,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee2ee5b5887098f155b85049bdd1c480b114a0ed","tid":1946869,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"捉埋呢兩個啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"係就快，即刻支爆。"},{"pid":"91196a3cd8822f375c7195b1a31fabec8a8888dc","tid":1946869,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"憑咩？ 有錢就可以罵黨？"},{"pid":"6937d383c342f321a21e95b7eb657ad77d9b3b27","tid":1946869,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"捉埋佢兩個"},{"pid":"e4750b1664c69db9e8691f